        <a href="/toolbox" class="nav-card">ğŸ§° å·¥å…·ç®± (Toolbox)</a>
        <a href="/status" class="nav-card">ğŸ“Š çŠ¶æ€ (Status)</a>
        <a href="/about" class="nav-card">ğŸ™‹ å…³äºæˆ‘ (About)</a>
